      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAMAL WICK (4) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Loco Miss (23.15) in a Grade 4/5. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Expecting another good run. HENDRIX (7) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 22.91 beating Domineering. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Will go close again if runs up to latest. CREEPING TIGER (2) is worth a look over a shorter distance this time.",
